Pylarion document:
http://pylarion-doc.rhev-ci-vms.eng.rdu2.redhat.com/

Certification Install:
1. wget http://password.corp.redhat.com/legacy.crt
2. sudo mv legacy.crt /etc/pki/ca-trust/source/anchors/newca.crt
3. sudo update-ca-trust extract

Pylarion install:
1. git clone https://code.engineering.redhat.com/gerrit/pylarion
2. python setup.py install
3. python setup.py bdist_rpm (If you want to make rpm package)
4. pip install --upgrade pip
5. pip install -r requirements.txt
